        <title>久石让在武道馆：与宫崎骏动画一同走过的25年</title>
        <link>https://jujushare.github.io/movies/%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90/%E4%B9%85%E7%9F%B3%E8%AE%A9%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A6%E9%81%93%E9%A6%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%AB%E5%B4%8E%E9%AA%8F%E5%8A%A8%E7%94%BB%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8C%E8%B5%B0%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%8425%E5%B9%B4/</link>
